!! addtiles

Generate a base map using [ext[OpenStreetMap|https://www.openstreetmap.org/]] in default which is equivalent with R function [ext[addTiles|https://rstudio.github.io/leaflet/reference/map-layers.html]].

!! Syntax

```
[addtiles[]]
```

|purpose |generate a base map layer |
|input	|no inputs |
|output |json string for base map layer |

!! Example

```
<$htmlwidgets type="leaflet" filter="[addtiles[]] +[leaflet[]]" />
```

<$htmlwidgets type="leaflet" filter="[addtiles[]] +[leaflet[]]" />

If `addtiles` is missing in the whole filter, the default [ext[OpenStreetMap|https://www.openstreetmap.org/]] will be used.



```
<$htmlwidgets type="leaflet" filter="[leaflet[]]" />
```

<$htmlwidgets type="leaflet" filter="[leaflet[]]" />

